(37926, 'Iride Akatsuki has unlocked hidden content in the game he\'s playing, \'Nakanohito Genome,\' and it turns out that this content is a real-life game! He soon wakes up to find that he has been kidnapped and taken to a strange place, along with a number of other teammates. Each of them specializes in a certain sort of game, like cultivation games, fighting games, puzzle games, etc. A llama-headed \'teacher\' gathers them after level 1 is cleared to explain how the game will proceed. Will this group of gamers succeed, and make it back to their real lives? (Source: MangaHelpers)', '23 min per ep', 0, 12, 'Finished Airing', '2019-07-06 22:00:00', '2019-09-21 22:00:00', 'https://cdn.myanimelist.net/images/anime/1725/102251.jpg', 'PG-13 - Teens 13 or older', 'TV', 'Nakanohito Genome [Jikkyouchuu]', 'ナカノヒトゲノム【実況中】', 'https://www.youtube.com/embed/inuhrp9tBYM?enablejsapi=1&wmode=opaque&autoplay=0', 300),
